 until September 24th, 2019, Amazon Prime...
caption:
Get 12 Months of Nintendo Switch Online for FREE with an Amazon Prime Membership

Up until September 24th, 2019, Amazon Prime Members can get 12 months of Nintendo Switch Online for free via Twitch Prime. If you’re currently not an Amazon Prime Member, you can sign up to a free Amazon Prime 30-day trial and still be eligible for at least a 3 month Nintendo Switch Online membership - you will have to move on to a paid Amazon Prime Membership for an extra 9 months worth of Nintendo Switch Online.

  • Register here for a free Amazon Prime 30-day trial
  • Sign in to Twitch Prime using your new Amazon Prime credentials and click ‘Claim now’
